<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA54">
<l>vāṉō maṟikaṭalō mārutamō tīyakamō</l>
<l>kāṉō voruṅkiṟṟuṅ kaṇṭilamā lāṉīṉṟa</l>
<l>kaṉṟuyarat tāmeṟintu kāyutirttār tāḷpaṇintōm</l>
<l>vaṉṟuyarai yāvā maruṅku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whether in the sky, the sea, the wind, inside the fire</l>
<l>or in the forest, alltogether we don’t see, we who have humbled ourselves</l>
<l>before the feet of him who brought down the fruit by throwing, for it to be high,</l>
<l>the calf born by a cow, on [any] side, ah, [our] harsh misery.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
